        <solution>
          <p>
            The domain for <m>x</m> is <m>-1 \leq x \leq 1</m>. As <m>t</m> increases, the <m>y</m>-value keeps increasing in both the positive and negative directions. This is an expanding figure 8 like graph.
          </p>
